{
  "stem": "7093.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only know that I, I was very upset because I wanted to go with that group.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other thing was that I had one-- I tried later on going out illegally.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't manage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose it was-- well, after that, I still tried, from '42 onward.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean when, when, when I, I didn't manage to go legally, I tried illegally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't manage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yet, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know I tried that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the same time, I stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, when I was in Budapest, I stopped going to the Zionists-- to Zionist because I just didn't have time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I came home on holiday, I always took part still in the Zionist activities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't take part in any Zionist activities from '42 to '44 because I just simply haven't had the time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, which was the 19th of March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, by that time, I had this wonderful job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very badly paid, but I was extremely proud to have got it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I lived-- at that point, I lived in a Jewish hostel, where, where we had-- which was an orthodox hostel, actually.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got in there because I became very friendly with two girls, two Czech girls, who it turned out after the 19th March that they were there illegally under false names.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And actually, in the hostel, practically all of the girls who were there were illegally-- were with illegal papers, with false papers, and came from Bratislava and from the various territories where people have been deported already.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were Jewish, but they had false papers and lived under false names.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I became very friendly, and so I moved in with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
